IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. SEPARATE-IMAGE-CUBE-TEST.
ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
CONFIGURATION SECTION.
SPECIAL-NAMES.
    LOCAL-SIZE IS (1, 1, 1).
INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
FILE-CONTROL.
    SELECT TEX-CUBE ASSIGN TO "GPU-IMAGE-0-0"
        ORGANIZATION IS TEXTURE-CUBE.
    SELECT SMP-CUBE ASSIGN TO "GPU-SAMPLER-0-1"
        ORGANIZATION IS SAMPLER.
DATA DIVISION.
FILE SECTION.
FD  TEX-CUBE.
01  IMAGE-RECORD PIC V(4).
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01  UV-COORDS           PIC V(3).
01  RAW-PIXEL           PIC V(4).
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    MAIN-LOGIC.
        MOVE (1.0, 0.0, 0.0) TO UV-COORDS.
        READ TEX-CUBE WITH SMP-CUBE
            AT UV-COORDS 
            INTO RAW-PIXEL.
        GOBACK.
